Create abbreviations & expansions to help streamline repatitive tasks & reduce the need for copy/paste

example: if i enter the following into the program:

abv: zemail
text: example@hotmail.com

then the next time I type zemail, the system will change the word zemail to example@hotmail.com


Adding a snippet:
- Enter your abbreviation in the abbreviation field
- Enter the text you want the abbreviation to expand to in the text field
- Click "Add snippet" button

Deleting a snippet:
- Enter the abbreviaion in the abbreviation field
- Click the Delete snippet button (no need to enter the text)
